    "description": "Produced by neutralizing tartaric acid with sodium hydroxide or sodium carbonate. The degree of neutralization determines whether monosodium tartrate (E335i) or disodium tartrate (E335ii) is formed. Tartaric acid itself is typically obtained from wine industry byproducts."
